{"tid":1269460,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"我地冇軍訓，但係我地有打開機","createTime":"2019-06-30T14:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T08:20:06.000Z","uid":59450,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9594f7a0dec9b40455bb440b58e9153c24898046","tid":1269460,"uid":59450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"近排睇 傘上 遍地開花，舒琪導演有個有趣睇法，話呢代人因為打開機，所以將打機既果套搬咗去抗爭手法，又意外地有效。<br />\n諗落都係，我地又冇軍訓，又無組織，原本純粹9up，但係又突然可以短時間叫到啲人出黎，或者做好咗啲野周圍pub，好可能都係玩得rpg/mmorpg game 多。<br />\n一入隊，就分好每人角色同崗位；角色職責分明，互相配合；公會任一出周圍call 馬，上得既就上；唔夠打會上網傾策略，share 破關資訊；打機為咗贏，淨係諗贏，輸咗由佢，開過盤再黎過。<br />\n打機既策略思考、頭腦身手反應、同隊友既契合，全部都係打機練返黎，唯一問題係唔夠啲做gym嘅大隻囉😂<br />\n<br />\n所以話，細個唔聽老母講，日日打機，係好孩子嚟！"},{"pid":"367b1706bf1c6d3d8b29feab1069a1c87f042bef","tid":1269460,"uid":116374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:44:33.000Z","msg":"又好似岩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15018664884aaff78ac47773d447e2036819b5a8","tid":1269460,"uid":162783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:16:14.000Z","msg":"可惜係冇裝姐"},{"pid":"f1ff6f984037ad4442eff6c3915d79cc95374537","tid":1269460,"uid":266231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:16:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3d705dfa064d788420b41b7e3649d293f12fc88","tid":1269460,"uid":39974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T22:58:19.000Z","msg":"依排又興食雞呢 男男女女都有玩"},{"pid":"b7e3a5c6eb65e5f645ce7896c8f660e9644bbb26","tid":1269460,"uid":45498,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T23:31:03.000Z","msg":"玩mon hunt 最大得著係<br />\n唔好擋人輸出<br />\n否則肯定被削成人棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B0H9zZP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB0H9zZP.gif&h=adbb720b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.c